external_knowledge:
- The term "top-rated products" refers to products with the highest average rating given by users; 
- "most preferred features" refers to the features that have been preferred by the largest number of users;
- Average rating is a measure of how well a product is liked by users, with higher ratings indicating better products.

sql:
SELECT user_name
FROM users
WHERE user_id IN (
  SELECT user_id
  FROM comparisons
);
